                    <span>I have purchased this book a few weeks ago and think its great. Brief explanations and to the point. I am just learning Java and I can quickly find help when I need it. It makes a great desktop reference.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Good format! Simple (to adapt) code, helped me get going</div>
                    <div>
